agent-sandbox v0.4.6

Upstream release/repo: https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/agent-sandbox
Release tag:           v0.4.6  (https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/agent-sandbox/releases/tag/v0.4.6)
Controller image:      registry.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/agent-sandbox-controller:v0.4.6

manifest.yaml in this directory is the helm-rendered install of the upstream
chart, pinned to the controller image tag above and with leader election
DISABLED (single-replica single-node controller — leader election only adds a Lease
dependency and slows startup). It is VENDORED: edit upstream + re-render, never
hand-edit manifest.yaml.

Regenerate with (run against a checkout of the upstream repo at tag v0.4.6):

    helm template agent-sandbox ./charts/agent-sandbox \
        --namespace agent-sandbox-system \
        --include-crds \
        --set image.tag=v0.4.6 \
        --set controller.leaderElect=false \
        > manifest.yaml

Notes:
  - --include-crds keeps the Sandbox CRD (sandboxes.agents.x-k8s.io, group
    agents.x-k8s.io) in the same file so a single `kubectl apply` installs both
    the CRD and the controller Deployment (agent-sandbox-controller in ns
    agent-sandbox-system).
  - The chart path / value keys above match upstream v0.4.6; if a future bump
    renames them, update this file alongside the regenerated manifest.
